  • Classes in ch.zhaw.iamp.rct.grammar used by ch.zhaw.iamp.rct.grammar 
    Class and Description
    GrammarParser
    This parser parses the grammar text, entered in the upper left text area in the Grammar Window.
    GrammarParser.Keyword
    A keyword is used to specify what attribute is configured in the initialization area.
    GrammarParser.Option
    Options are like GrammarParser.Keywords, but accept only boolean values (true and false).
    Parser
    A Parser takes a given text and parses it.
    ParserError
    A ParserError may be produced by a Parser when parsing text.
    Range
    Represents a range between a minimal and a maximal value.
    Rule
    A rule defines how a letter should be replaced when an initialization string evolves.
